description:
LogM: Table containing Ericsson-specific LogM data including timestamp, location, cell identifiers, and various metadata fields.

dateTime: Timestamp of the log entry.  Area_Name: Geographic area of the cell. CellId: Unique identifier for the cell site. Id2: Redundant cell identifier. Id3:  Likely an additional identifier, currently only containing '1'. vsDataType: Data type identifier ('vsDataLogM'). vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the Ericsson-specific data format. LogM.logMId:  Log message identifier. LogM.nodeCredential:  Node credentials (currently empty). LogM.trustCategory: Trust category (currently empty). LogM.reportProgress: Report progress status (currently empty).
